      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PROUD CHOICE (5) has missed the frame at his last two but did run well three back when second (23.27) in a Grade 5 at this track. Can make amends this time. POPPY'S DARLIN' (2) filled a minor placing last start at Richmond behind Harmony Keeping (18.55) in a Grade 5. Took the lead and boxed on but run over. Form from her last run is proving to be solid. Can feature again. KISS AND RUN (8) turned in a solid run last start over 272m at this track finishing 4th and beaten only 3 lengths (16.04). Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. Key runner on best form. MISS GRAHAM (1) has ability and can feature with the right run after missing a cheque here most recently.",
